headline: J.B. Hunt Transport Services, Inc. Announces First Quarter 2025 Earnings Release Date and Conference Call Information
summary: LOWELL, Ark., April 01, 2025--J.B. Hunt Transport Services, Inc., (NASDAQ: JBHT) announced today that it expects to issue first quarter 2025 earnings at the close of the market Tuesday, April 15, 2025. It will hold a conference call from 4:00-5:00 p.m. CDT on the same day to discuss the quarterly results and answer questions from the investment community.
